        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo and Mia were students who loved to spend time in the old town library.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 3.788
            },
            {
              "text": "One day, they found a dusty book which contained a hidden map.",
              "audioStart": 4.65,
              "audioEnd": 7.838
            },
            {
              "text": "This map showed a secret path that led to a cave high in the mountains.",
              "audioStart": 8.7,
              "audioEnd": 12.238
            },
            {
              "text": "If they reached the cave by sunset, they might find a great treasure.",
              "audioStart": 13.1,
              "audioEnd": 16.587
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The two friends walked quickly along the narrow road toward the high mountains.",
              "audioStart": 17.45,
              "audioEnd": 21.2
            },
            {
              "text": "After several hours, the sun began to fall behind the peaks.",
              "audioStart": 22.062,
              "audioEnd": 25.475
            },
            {
              "text": "Suddenly, they saw a row of blue stones that glowed in the dark.",
              "audioStart": 26.337,
              "audioEnd": 29.613
            },
            {
              "text": "These stones acted as a guide through the cold forest.",
              "audioStart": 30.475,
              "audioEnd": 33.188
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo wondered if they would ever find the treasure before night.",
              "audioStart": 34.05,
              "audioEnd": 36.962
            },
            {
              "text": "Mia told him that they should keep moving forward despite their fear.",
              "audioStart": 37.825,
              "audioEnd": 41.087
            },
            {
              "text": "They followed the blue light until they reached a small opening in the rock.",
              "audioStart": 41.95,
              "audioEnd": 45.325
            },
            {
              "text": "The cave was filled with golden objects which had been hidden for many years.",
              "audioStart": 46.188,
              "audioEnd": 49.85
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They realized that the treasure was more than just money.",
              "audioStart": 50.712,
              "audioEnd": 53.312
            },
            {
              "text": "It was a collection of history from a long time ago.",
              "audioStart": 54.175,
              "audioEnd": 56.737
            },
            {
              "text": "If they had not followed the stones, this secret would remain lost forever.",
              "audioStart": 57.6,
              "audioEnd": 61.362
            },
            {
              "text": "They felt very proud because they had completed the difficult task.",
              "audioStart": 62.225,
              "audioEnd": 65.513
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The sun finally disappeared, so the cave became very dark.",
              "audioStart": 66.375,
              "audioEnd": 69.85
            },
            {
              "text": "They used their lights to look at the beautiful items one last time.",
              "audioStart": 70.713,
              "audioEnd": 74.05
            },
            {
              "text": "Everything they saw was perfect and filled with mystery.",
              "audioStart": 74.912,
              "audioEnd": 77.638
            },
            {
              "text": "Finally, the two friends decided to return home before it was too late.",
              "audioStart": 78.5,
